{
  "texts": [
    "This is due to the 25-min time limit for the first part of the analysis task.",
    "In the second part of the analysis task, participants were asked to indicate the probability of pre-formulated propositions.",
    "They were also asked to indicate how confident they were that their assessment was correct based on the sources.",
    "Participants' assessments of probability and confidence in the second part of the analysis task were also evaluated by comparison with the experts' assessments.",
    "As these can be compared directly, no scoring standard is needed here."
  ]
}